This directory should contain the following items:

- minfi_6ct.csv
  contains cytosine panel used for 6-cell-type deconvolutoin calculated by minfi
  obtained from:  extracted manually after running minfi cell count estimation on the blueprint dataset
  located under:  provided in this repository
  exact address:  data/Minfi/minfi_6ct.csv

- minfi_12ct.csv
  contains cytosine panel used for 12-cell-type deconvolutoin calculated by minfi
  obtained from:  extracted manually after running minfi cell count estimation on the blueprint dataset
  located under:  provided in this repository
  exact address:  data/Minfi/minfi_12ct.csv
